Class AbstractPartnerProxy

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.poesys.db.dto.AbstractLazyLoadingDtoProxy
      • org.phoenixbioinformatics.api.db.api.AbstractPartnerProxy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.poesys.db.dto.IDbDto, com.poesys.db.dto.IObserver, com.poesys.db.dto.ISubject, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<com.poesys.db.dto.IDbDto>, IPartner
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    PartnerProxy

    public abstract class AbstractPartnerProxy
extends com.poesys.db.dto.AbstractLazyLoadingDtoProxy
implements IPartner

    A data-access layer data-transfer object (DTO) lazy-loading proxy for the Partner. This class is an abstract class that contains AndroMDA generated code; change nothing in this class. Instead, override any methods in the concrete subclass generated in the same package. AndroMDA will overwrite this class each time you run it but will never overwrite the concrete subclass.

    a system that comprises a unit for subscription, authentication, and authorization

    Author:
    Poesys/DB Cartridge
